  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defend your farm</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing day at the farm. But what is this? Where does this rat come from? Kitty grabs a fish and after a few throws... the rat is gone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/16f2ce6be139ebd17f34684619cdf93f.poster.avif?t=1742234442\" width=600 height=68 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/16f2ce6be139ebd17f34684619cdf93f.webm?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/16f2ce6be139ebd17f34684619cdf93f.mp4?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get stronger</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More enemies are approaching, but Kitty is improving, too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/e7df03a230ef7315ab6fca0df468acce.poster.avif?t=1742234442\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/e7df03a230ef7315ab6fca0df468acce.webm?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/e7df03a230ef7315ab6fca0df468acce.mp4?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock Skills</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And Kitty isn’t alone! Recruit other animals from the farm, like Stompy the bull, to join the fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/55b138a5941fdc2a28f3131c74088425.poster.avif?t=1742234442\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/55b138a5941fdc2a28f3131c74088425.webm?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/55b138a5941fdc2a28f3131c74088425.mp4?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Permanent Upgrades</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The farm didn’t hold. Let’s give it another try, but this time with some upgrades. Kitty collected enough daisies to unlock improvements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/785d6e0b6820bdaa74204fed39051455.poster.avif?t=1742234442\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/785d6e0b6820bdaa74204fed39051455.webm?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/785d6e0b6820bdaa74204fed39051455.mp4?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock Characters</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maybe a friend can help? Let’s defend the farm with Fluffy, the electrifying sheep!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/46049b6ebd846e7d3c5c3ce028646bda.poster.avif?t=1742234442\" width=600 height=54 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/46049b6ebd846e7d3c5c3ce028646bda.webm?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/46049b6ebd846e7d3c5c3ce028646bda.mp4?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight Back</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s time to fully upgrade and fight back stronger than ever!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/2c1e9520c3722a4f04fcff755a4d38ee.poster.avif?t=1742234442\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/2c1e9520c3722a4f04fcff755a4d38ee.webm?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/2c1e9520c3722a4f04fcff755a4d38ee.mp4?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Five lanes</strong> of frantic fun, full of enemies attacking your farm.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Six skills</strong> to master and deploy in each run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Short runs</strong> of 5-10 minutes packed with action.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Five unlockable characters</strong> with unique abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Six permanent upgrades</strong> to unlock for long-term progression.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dozens of different enemies</strong> and challenging bosses.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to defend your farm? Kitty and her friends are counting on you!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defend your farm</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing day at the farm. But what is this? Where does this rat come from? Kitty grabs a fish and after a few throws... the rat is gone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/16f2ce6be139ebd17f34684619cdf93f.poster.avif?t=1742234442\" width=600 height=68 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/16f2ce6be139ebd17f34684619cdf93f.webm?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/16f2ce6be139ebd17f34684619cdf93f.mp4?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get stronger</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More enemies are approaching, but Kitty is improving, too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/e7df03a230ef7315ab6fca0df468acce.poster.avif?t=1742234442\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/e7df03a230ef7315ab6fca0df468acce.webm?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252160/extras/e7df03a230ef7315ab6fca0df468acce.mp4?t=1742234442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock Skills</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And Kitty isn’t alone! Recruit other animals from the farm, like Stompy the bull, to join the fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_